    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, but it came to a point I couldn't talk anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why did you decide you want to tell your story now?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I always want people to know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I want my children to and my grandchildren, you know-- people has to know this story.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Because it was no reason to do something like that to people what they didn't do anything wrong.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I try my best for my children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [CRYING] I don't know how to answer this question.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I tried the best to do the best for them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't want them to, to go through [SOBBING] what we went through.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
